ggplot()  +
  annotate("rect", 
           xmin = lubridate::as_datetime("2017-01-09 00:58:00") + hours(2),
           xmax = lubridate::as_datetime("2017-01-09 02:58:00") + hours(2),
           ymin = 0,
           ymax = Inf,
           alpha = 0.1,
           fill = "red") + 
  geom_freqpoly(data = dplyr::filter(df_second, has_hudson == T), aes(x = date, colour = "h"), binwidth = 500)
